The paper deals with enhancing the resolution of light field images using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of light field imaging also suggests that the paper could be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under multiple sub-categories such as multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
